node.text: Perfect views and best place in the world!! ❤️❤️❤️❤️
@elise_the_gsd 😎😎😎

If not for #covid19, Merlion Park would be bustling with tourists, it would have been near impossible for mummy to take such beautiful videos. I hope you’ll enjoy these great views of the Marina Downtown area as much as I enjoyed my #bicycle 🚲 ride with mummy — except the part where we were going downslope and she was still busy taking video 2️⃣ balancing with one hand! 😱
Anyways, the world is a different place now and it would be a long while before life returns to the way we knew it. Even then, it won’t be exactly the same again. Wherever you are, I hope you are staying safe and healthy ❤️
